{"title":"苹果官方鼠标移动速度慢问题解决(Magic Mouse)","date":"2022-01-05T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年1月5日","L":"2022/01/05","MM-DD":"01-05"},"link":"magic-mouse","tags":["Mac"],"categories":["Mac"],"updated":"2022-01-04T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"设置\">设置<a title=\"#设置\" href=\"#设置\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/626cad73239250f7c5d61401.png\" alt=\"Magic Mouse\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><strong>如果这里的调节到最大还是满足不了你</strong></p>\n<p><strong>我们可以通过终端查看到我们鼠标的设置：</strong></p>\n<p>读取当前的移动速度：<br>\n<code>defaults read -g com.apple.mouse.scaling</code></p>\n<p>默认可能是：<code>3</code> ， 我这里设置的：<code>7</code></p>\n<p><code>defaults write -g com.apple.mouse.scaling 7</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"重启电脑生效\">重启电脑生效<a title=\"#重启电脑生效\" href=\"#重启电脑生效\"></a></h3>\n","prev":{"title":"iOS App苹果企业签分发","link":"ios-app-enterprise-sign-share"},"next":{"title":"Redis 配置文件说明","link":"redis-config-explan"},"plink":"http://l-zm.com/magic-mouse/","toc":[{"id":"设置","title":"设置","index":"1"},{"id":"重启电脑生效","title":"重启电脑生效","index":"2"}],"reading_time":"89 字约 1 分钟"}